Package: eva-relay
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.12-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Eva Relay Server - Store-and-forward message relay
 Eva relay server for offline message delivery. Stores encrypted messages
 until recipients come online.
 .
 Features:
  - WebSocket protocol (ws/wss)
  - SQLite message storage with AES-256-GCM encryption
  - Federation with peer relays
  - CBNP cover traffic (optional)
  - Mix routing delays for metadata protection
Depends: libssl3, libsqlite3-0
Section: net
Priority: optional